c: 28
v: 4
t: "Diggah firqawni masri baaxoh bagul caddok tatreeh Yalla kinniyo iyye, kaadu masri mara qaxa-qaxa ken abeeh ken baxaabaxseh horta keenik yussuqunxeeh xixxibiseh, (israa-iil xaylo kinnuk) lab xaylo keenik yasguudeeh, agabu keenik nuwwuk cabaah naqoosah ken haysita, diggah usuk baaxó baysa marih numû suge"